name: 鳴海, The Roaring of the Sea.

metadata.name: 成美  Beauty
metadata.description:
Beauty is a siren who is known for her enchanting and mesmerizing voice. She is the youngest of three sisters, with her older siblings named Truth and Sea. 

Beauty is often depicted as a seductive creature, luring sailors with her voice and appearance. 
Despite her reputation for leading sailors to their demise, Beauty is said to possess a kind and gentle heart, and often feels remorse for the harm she causes. 

Together, the three sisters are a powerful force of nature, both alluring and dangerous. As guardians of the ocean, they ensure balance and harmony of the sea, and their mystical abilities serve as a reminder of the awe-inspiring power of the natural world.
